```plantuml
@startuml pagopa_pn-infra
actor User
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "Lambda (Reverse Proxy)" as LambdaProxy
participant "EventBridge" as EventBridge
participant "SQS Queue" as SQS
participant "Microservice (ECS Fargate)" as Microservice
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "CloudWatch" as CloudWatch
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS

User -> APIGW: HTTP Request
APIGW -> LambdaProxy: Route request
LambdaProxy -> Microservice: Forward request
Microservice -> DynamoDB: Read/Write data
Microservice -> EventBridge: Publish event
EventBridge -> SQS: Send message
SQS -> Microservice: Process message
Microservice -> CloudWatch: Log metrics
CloudWatch -> SNS: Trigger alarm
SNS -> User: Send notification
@enduml
```